      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "俞伯牙引童儿同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00002",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "好访名贤，顾不得，涉水登山。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00003",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "春去夏来速转寒，分别不觉又一年。撇乡只因访故友，哪怕涉水与登山。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00004",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "下官姓俞名瑞字伯牙，乃鲁国人氏，在晋国为官，官拜上大夫之职。只因去岁催贡而归，闲游马鞍山前，偶遇樵夫种子期贤弟。我二人共谈琴律，彼此相投，故而结为金兰之好。分别之时，赠他黄金二笏，约定今秋还在马鞍山前相会。来到此处，不见贤弟到来，不免我去到集贤村访他便了。童儿，",
      "text_length": 131
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00005",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "童儿允。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00006",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "携定瑶琴，随我到集贤村去者。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00007",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "童儿"
      ],
      "text": "遵命！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00008",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "我二人在山前相逢甚好，钟贤弟不到来所为哪条？莫不是在家中奉养二老，因此上与朋友失信今朝？叫童儿你与我向前引道，但愿得集贤村访见故交。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00009",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "童儿引俞伯牙同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00010",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "钟元甫上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00011",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "屋漏更遭连夜雨，行船偏遇打头风。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00012",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "老汉钟元甫。所生一儿，名叫子期。只因去岁在马鞍山前砍樵，偶遇晋国大夫俞伯牙。他二人共谈琴律，情投意合，结为金兰之好。临别之时，又赠吾儿黄金二笏。约定今秋还在马鞍山前相会。我儿回得家来，白日砍柴，夜晚攻书，朝思暮想，偶得病症而亡。今乃百日之期，老汉备得纸钱，去到坟前烧化，以表父子之情。正是：",
      "text_length": 145
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00013",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "家有万贯终何用，老来无子落场空。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00014",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "老眼昏花路难寻，耳听得树林内百鸟喧声。乌鸦也有反哺意，羊羔也有跪乳情。黄梅未落青梅解，白发人反送儿黑发身。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00015",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "钟元甫下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00016",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "俞伯牙、童儿同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00017",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "昨晚间抚瑶琴内藏悲调，抚不着钟子期所为哪条？将身儿来至在双阳岔道，但不知集贤村路走哪条？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00018",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "且住，来此双阳岔道，但不知哪条道路，可通集贤村？那旁有一老丈，等他到来，问个明白。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00019",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "钟元甫上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00020",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "断香烟绝后代此罪非小，可叹我年迈人无有下梢。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00021",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "老丈请了！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00022",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "客官请了！敢是迷失路径？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00023",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00024",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "问的何处？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00025",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "请问老丈，此地可有一集贤村么？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00026",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "客官你来看，东十里也是集贤村，西十里也是集贤村，但未知问的哪个集贤村？",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00027",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "老丈你且少待。哎吓，贤弟，既有两个集贤村，为何不对愚兄说明，叫我哪里去问？",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00028",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "客官背地沉吟，敢是指路不明？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00029",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00030",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "老汉居住有数年，无有不是亲朋。但不知问的哪一家？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00031",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "拜访钟子期贤弟。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00032",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "你待怎讲？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00033",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "钟子期！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00034",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "听说提起子期话，不由老汉泪如麻。我儿常说俞伯牙，不知是他不是他？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00035",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "客官你来迟了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00036",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "怎么来迟了？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00037",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "客官有所不知：老汉钟元甫，亡儿子期，只因去岁在马鞍山前砍樵，偶遇着晋国大夫俞什么……",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00038",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "敢是俞伯牙？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00039",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "不错，俞伯牙！他二人共谈琴律，彼此相投，结为金兰之好；临行之时，赠他黄金二笏，约定今秋还在马鞍山前相会。我儿回到家来，白日砍樵，夜晚读书，心思过度，偶得病症而亡了！",
      "text_length": 82
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00040",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "你才怎讲？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00041",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "一命亡了！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00042",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟！子期！哎贤弟吓！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00043",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "吓，此位何人？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00044",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "童儿"
      ],
      "text": "此乃是晋国上大夫俞大人便是。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00045",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "听说是钟贤弟把命丧了，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00046",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "俞伯牙晕。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00047",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀大人醒来，大人醒来！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00048",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "俞伯牙醒。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00049",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟！子期！哎呀贤弟吓！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00050",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "我腹内好一似万把钢刀。他的父即我父双膝跪倒，",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00051",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "问答人施一礼所为哪条？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00052",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "我就是俞伯牙伯父不晓，贤弟死留何言细说根苗。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00053",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "我的儿临死前亦曾言道：埋至在马鞍山候驾来瞧。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00054",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "既如此老伯父向前引道，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00055",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "随我来。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00056",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "这就是新坟台不孝儿曹。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00057",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟！子期！哎呀贤弟吓……",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00058",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "见坟台不由人双膝跪倒，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00059",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟！子期！哎呀贤弟吓……",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00060",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "我心中好一似走马断桥。哭一声钟贤弟何方去了？可怜我万水千山空走一遭。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00061",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "吓伯父，侄儿在此一祭。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00062",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "老汉代谢。儿吓，俞大人前来祭奠与你吓！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00063",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "童儿，将瑶琴摆在坟前。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00064",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "童儿允，摆琴。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00065",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "正是：",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00066",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "来此空枉费，人情赴东流。只因渺茫去，存留土一丘。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00067",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢三眼",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "想去岁在山前论琴交好，曾结拜如同那一母同胞。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00068",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄快三眼",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "分别时约定了今秋来到，因此上辞王驾来走一遭。兄为你二双亲不能尽孝，兄为你不愿穿平带蟒袍。钟贤弟在阴曹你可知晓？有几代古圣贤细听根苗：孔圣人哭颜回皆因丧早，齐景公哭吴婴君臣相交；鲁公子哭下惠朋友至好，羊角哀亦哭过左伯桃。前辈的古圣贤也能比到，俞伯牙哭子期皆因是，想去岁闲游在马鞍山道，谈谈讲讲，论论琴调。哭一声钟贤弟何方去了！",
      "text_length": 162
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00069",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "渔夫、樵夫同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00070",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "渔夫"
      ],
      "text": "六月炉边炼铁，数九江上渔翁。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00071",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "樵夫"
      ],
      "text": "非是不知寒暑，生涯落在其中。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00072",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "渔夫",
        "樵夫"
      ],
      "text": "请了请了，你我无事，看此人讲些什么。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00073",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "俞伯牙抚琴。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00074",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "渔夫",
        "樵夫"
      ],
      "text": "看此人对着坟前，不知弄什么。你我好笑吓，哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00075",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "渔夫、樵夫同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00076",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "伯父，他二人为何发笑而去？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00077",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "他二人不晓琴律，故而发笑而去。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00078",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "听说是二渔樵琴律不晓，不由我俞伯牙心似火烧。我只得将瑶琴摔碎不要，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00079",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "俞伯牙摔琴。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00080",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "问大人摔此琴所为哪条？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00081",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "摔碎瑶琴凤尾寒，子期不再对谁弹。春风满面皆朋友，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00082",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "三叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟！子期！贤弟吓！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00083",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "要想知音难上难了！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00084",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "问伯父贤弟死家有何靠？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00085",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "祖居在集贤村家业萧条。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00086",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "叫童儿取黄金伯父养老，与贤弟春秋祭买纸烧化。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00087",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀大人，慢说小老儿，就是亡儿子期，亦感恩非浅。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00088",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "辞伯父，别子期，扬长就道，可叹他年迈人无有下梢。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00089",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "吓伯父，侄到家去，差人迎接伯父伯母，那时不要推辞。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00090",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "相逢不久分别早，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00091",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "他二人结拜如同胞。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00092",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "伯牙在，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00093",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "子期死呀……",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00094",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "俞伯牙、钟元甫同哭。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00095",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "再与伯父说根苗。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00096",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "伯父，侄儿走后，不要想他了。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00097",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "吾不想他。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00098",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "子期是我。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00099",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "不敢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00100",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "我是子期。告辞了！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00101",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "俞伯牙"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟！子期！哎呀贤弟吓……",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00102",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "俞伯牙下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00103",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "送大人。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00104",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "子期儿吓！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00105",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "似这等金兰友世间少有，回家去与妈妈细说根苗。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00106",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 106,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "text": "儿吓……",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01010001_e00107",
      "play_id": "01010001",
      "scene_id": "01010001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 107,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "钟元甫下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}